data.description: Charming maintenance free ranch townhome located in the Aspen Trail subdivision. Two bedrms, two baths, dining rm, living rm,den/study and large country kitchen. All of the windows have custom shades (curtains and hardware stay). Many upgrades throughout, ceramic floors in kitchen, laundry room, foyer and bathrooms. Maple cabinets and finished garage with attic stairway, every room has solid six panel doors. Large private patio with landscaping surrounding the home.  3 Sun tunnel skylights.
data.whatILove: It is on a cul-de-sac and the neighbors are nice and friendly.  Walking distance from a kids play park and water sprinkler park.
